&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We are looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Performance Marketing Manager&lt;/strong&gt; to lead and coordinate InvGate’s paid media strategy and execution. This role will own the planning, execution, optimization, and performance analysis of all paid acquisition campaigns, working closely with our external paid media agency and internal teams (Content, Design, RevOps, and Product Marketing).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
