&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;We are looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Senior &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;Product Manager&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;to join our Product team. This team plays a key role in shaping the future of our solutions—leading discovery, defining functionality, and managing the full lifecycle of new features in alignment with our product strategy and roadmap.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;Core Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;p-rich_text_list p-rich_text_list__bullet p-rich_text_list--nested&quot; data-stringify-type=&quot;unordered-list&quot; data-list-tree=&quot;true&quot; data-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;
