&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Own features end-to-end—from discovery and scoping to launch and iteration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Create clear and comprehensive functional specifications and other product documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Collaborate closely with Engineering and Design/UX to ensure high-quality, timely, and cost-effective delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Inspire and empower cross-functional partners to build strong collaboration practices and deliver exceptional products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Actively contribute to the evolution of the product roadmap, bringing insights from customer feedback, market analysis, and internal stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Serve as a product reference across multiple teams—Sales, Customer Success, Technical Support, Marketing, and more—facilitating alignment and knowledge sharing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;What We’re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;We’re seeking a highly curious, methodical, and analytical professional &lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;with vast experience in product analysis or product management within a SaaS environment&lt;/span&gt;. Someone comfortable acting as a bridge between technical and non-technical audiences, and who thrives on understanding complex problems and translating them into clear, actionable solutions.&lt;br&gt;Given the nature of our products, experience or familiarity with&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;IT operations, infrastructure environments, service management frameworks&lt;/strong&gt;, or methodologies such as&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;ITIL&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;is highly valued.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&q

&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;InvGate &lt;/strong&gt;is a leading software company providing solutions for Service and Asset Management to thousands of companies across 70 countries. We are seeking a strategic-minded Product Marketing Manager to join our team. If you have a blend of creativity, technical understanding, and strategic thinking, we want to hear from you.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;As a &lt;strong&gt;Product Marketing Manager&lt;/strong&gt; at InvGate you will be at the forefront of shaping and communicating the value of our products. This role involves leading the positioning and messaging strategy, creating impactful collateral, and maintaining open communication channels with our Product, Sales, Marketing and Customer Success teams.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Positioning &amp;amp; Messaging Strategy:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the positioning &amp;amp; messaging strategy for InvGate Asset Management solutions, aligning with company guidelines and brand positioning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teams to ensure consistency and accuracy in product messaging across all channels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collateral &amp;amp; Website Updates:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keep collateral up-to-date with the latest product features, benefits, and positioning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create interactive product demos to showcase the most appealing use cases our clients and prospects are looking for.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the Marketing team to craft copy for the company website, ensuring alignment with overall marketing and product messaging.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with design and content teams to create collateral that resonates with target audiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bridge Product and Business:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keep a regular cadence with Product teams to stay informed about product usage, enhancements, and roadmap.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be the “Voice of the Customer” for the product team conducting customer interviews, doing research and talking to industry experts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a liaison between GTM teams and Product teams, ensuring our go-to-market strategies align with product development timelines and goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive Enablement:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct ongoing competitive analysis (you’ll have access to Klue) to understand market trends, positioning, and messaging strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use insights gained to refine and enhance InvGate&#39;s product messaging for a competitive edge.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Qualifications:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bilingual - English and Spanish&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience in Product Marketing or transferable skills, preferably in the B2B software or technology industry.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong written and verbal communication skills with the ability to translate technical concepts into compelling messaging.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to multitask, prioritize, and manage time effectively in a fast-paced environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to collaborate effectively with cross-functional teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience launching a Product or Start-up is a big plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;em&gt;Our benefits include career development opportunities, English lessons and extended PTO.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Our office is located in Belgrano, CABA. This position will be &lt;strong&gt;Hybrid&lt;/strong&gt;, requiring office attendance at least twice a week if you are in AMBA/CABA.&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;A &lt;/em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;InvGate&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt; é uma empresa SaaS em rápido crescimento que desenvolve produtos para&lt;/em&gt; &lt;strong&gt;gestão de TI e automação de serviços&lt;/strong&gt;, utilizados por clientes em mais de &lt;strong&gt;60 países&lt;/strong&gt;, em setores como &lt;strong&gt;bancos, e-commerce, educação e tecnologia&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Para apoiar nosso crescimento contínuo, estamos buscando um(a) &lt;strong&gt;Sales &amp;amp; Implementation Engineer bilíngue&lt;/strong&gt; para se juntar ao nosso time.&lt;br&gt;Esta é uma posição &lt;strong&gt;estratégica e customer-facing&lt;/strong&gt;, responsável por entender os processos de negócio dos clientes e traduzi-los em soluções eficazes utilizando nossos produtos.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Neste papel, você atuará tanto no &lt;strong&gt;suporte técnico ao processo de vendas&lt;/strong&gt; quanto na &lt;strong&gt;implementação das soluções&lt;/strong&gt;, garantindo que os clientes extraiam o máximo valor das ofertas da InvGate.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Suas responsabilidades incluirão:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Entregar soluções técnicas para prospects e clientes nas áreas de &lt;strong&gt;ITSM e ITAM&lt;/strong&gt;, incluindo &lt;strong&gt;demonstrações de produto, proofs of concept (POCs)&lt;/strong&gt; e implementações em ambiente produtivo.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Validar as soluções propostas a prospects, considerando aspectos &lt;strong&gt;técnicos e de planejamento de projeto&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apoiar os &lt;strong&gt;Sales Representatives&lt;/strong&gt; durante todo o ciclo de vendas, desde &lt;strong&gt;RFI e RFP&lt;/strong&gt; até negociação contratual e fechamento.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Produzir documentação técnica para facilitar configurações, incluindo &lt;strong&gt;boas práticas de implementação&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Atuar como ponto de interface entre clientes e os times de &lt;strong&gt;Produto e P&amp;amp;D (R&amp;amp;D)&lt;/strong&gt;, apoiando a resolução de questões técnicas complexas ou desafios de implementação.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Não hesite em se candidatar se você:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Possui perfil &lt;strong&gt;analítico&lt;/strong&gt; e estruturado para resolução de problemas.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Possui formação completa ou em andamento em &lt;strong&gt;Engenharia, Ciência da Computação ou áreas correlatas&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tem &lt;strong&gt;fortes habilidades de comunicação&lt;/strong&gt; e consegue explicar conceitos técnicos de forma clara para públicos não técnicos.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gosta de trabalhar com clientes, demonstra boa energia, empatia e foco em solução.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Possui experiência prévia em &lt;strong&gt;implementação de software&lt;/strong&gt;, preferencialmente em soluções de &lt;strong&gt;ITSM, ITAM ou frameworks como ITIL&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Possui inglês &lt;strong&gt;ou&lt;/strong&gt; espanhol em nível avançado ou fluente (fluência em pelo menos um desses idiomas é obrigatória).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;O que oferecemos&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Uma posição estratégica com alto impacto no crescimento da empresa.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Autonomia e visibilidade regional.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oportunidades de desenvolvimento profissional em um ambiente internacional.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Aulas de inglês, treinamentos técnicos internos e externos, entre outros benefícios.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
